    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シェリア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cheria</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>チェスター</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chester</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル、あっスベル！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel! Don't Aslipel!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>"Suberu" means "to slip", which relies on Asbel's katakana pronunciation, Asuberu.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ？　なにを言っているんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Did you say something just now?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>忠告してくれてるのかしら？
スベルから気をつけるように</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is he trying to give us some kind of warning?
Something about us slipping and falling, maybe?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル、あっスベル！
アスベル、うまい事スベッてくれ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel, Aslipel!
Slip in an Asbrilliant way!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Here he uses "umai", meaning skilled, expertly, etc. I could go with Askilled or Asbexpertly just as easily.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>な、なんだと！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What did you just say?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕はアスベルをあっ、とスベらせてみせる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll make him Aslipel, and he'll go, "ahhh!"!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>させるものか！
俺は、自分の足腰を守ってみせる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh no you don't!
I'll protect my legs and back from you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだな。足腰は大事だもんな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As you should. Our back and legs are important,,,</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
